plot: As the Super Friends brave the Phantom Zone to bring Supergirl home, each member of the team is confronted by visions of their worst fear.

Supergirl falls victim to the Phantoms' Fear Visions, and it's up to Zor-El to keep her from falling permanently into despair. Meanwhile, the others fly the Tower into the Zone and must face their own personal fears if they're to find and rescue Supergirl.—Gislef
